These are Puzzles for 7x2 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 7x2-Level-1-1::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: 7up, milk
The people have 2 different hobbies: skydiving, magic-tricks
The people have 2 different jobs:  dancer, librarian
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: zombie, spy
There are 2 different nationalities: turkish, australian
2 different pets are kept: goldfish, cat
The people use 2 different means of transport: car, trike
1. the person drinking 7up is on the far right##1
2. the librarian is on the far right##1
3. the person driving the trike is on the left of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
4. the owner of the goldfish is the australian##1
5. the person watching spy movies is on the far left##1
6. the owner of the cat is on the right of the person driving the trike##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |
| Beverage      | milk     | 7up       |
| Hobby         | skydiving   | magic-tricks     |
| Job           | dancer | librarian   |
| Movie-Genre   | spy   | zombie  |
| Nationality   | australian | turkish |
| Pet           | goldfish      | cat     |
| Transport     | trike    | car   |

