.:: Puzzle 7x2-Level-1-2::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, 7up
The people have 2 different hobbies: chess, collecting
The people have 2 different jobs:  videographer, designer
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: disco, funk
There are 2 different nationalities: spanish, colombian
2 different pets are kept: goat, goldfish
The people use 2 different means of transport: scooter, airplane
1. the designer is on the right of the person who's hobby is collecting##1
2. the owner of the goldfish is the person driving the airplane##1
3. the person driving the scooter is on the left of the fan of disco##1
4. the colombian is on the far right##1
5. the person drinking hot-chocolate is the owner of the goat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |    2     |
| Beverage      | hot-chocolate    | 7up |
| Hobby         | collecting        | chess  |
| Job           | videographer | designer  |
| Music-Genre   | funk            | disco    |
| Nationality   | spanish     | colombian   |
| Pet           | goat         | goldfish    |
| Transport     | scooter           | airplane      |

